dc_title_s: New map of New York City.: From the latest surveys showing all the ferries and steamship docks, elevated, subways electric and cross town car lines.; New reference map and guide to New York City
dc_description_s: Compliments of the Broadway Central Hotel, New York. Text on verso. col. map.; 49 x 31 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
